{{Infobox nerve|Name=前庭神经节|Latin=ganglion vestibulare <br> ganglion Scarpae|Image=|Caption=|Image2=|Caption2=|Innervates=|BranchFrom=|BranchTo=}}'''前庭神经节'''（英文：Vestibular ganglion），是[[前庭神经|前庭神经]]的[[神经节|神经节]]，位于[[内耳道|内耳道]]中<ref name=":0">{{Cite book|chapter=Anatomy, Head and Neck, Ear Internal Auditory Canal (Internal Auditory Meatus, Internal Acoustic Canal)|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK544288/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=31335008|first=Kush|last=Panara|first2=Michael|last2=Hoffer}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Scarpa's Ganglion - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/veterinary-science-and-veterinary-medicine/scarpas-ganglion|accessdate=2021-03-11|work=|publisher=Science Direct|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Vestibular ganglion {{!}} Radiology Reference Article {{!}} Radiopaedia.org|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/vestibular-ganglion?lang=us|accessdate=2021-03-11|last=Hacking|first=Craig|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502065726/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/vestibular-ganglion?lang=us|dead-url=no}}</ref>。前庭神经节又被称为“斯卡帕神经节（Scarpa's ganglion）”，以纪念[[意大利|意大利]]解剖学家[[安东尼奥·斯卡帕|安东尼奥·斯卡帕]]<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Antonio Scarpa (1752–1832)|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3566389/|last=Grzybowski|first=Andrzej|last2=Sak|first2=Jarosław|date=2013|journal=Journal of Neurology|issue=2|doi=10.1007/s00415-012-6658-4|volume=260|pages=695–696|issn=0340-5354|pmc=3566389|pmid=22926229|access-date=2021-03-11|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111162043/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3566389/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

前庭神经节内含有[[雙極神經元|双极神经元]]的[[细胞体|细胞体]]，这些细胞体的长[[轴突|轴突]]（[[传入神经纤维|传入神经纤维]]）与[[前庭系统|前庭系统]]内的[[毛细胞|毛细胞]]（[[平衡觉|平衡觉]][[感受器|感受器]]）形成的[[突触|突触]]连接<ref name=":1" />。这包括位于[[半规管|半规管]]内以及[[耳前庭|耳前庭]]（[[球囊|球囊]]、[[椭圆囊|椭圆囊]]）内的毛细胞<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" />。

前庭神经节的大小在人出生时就基本定型<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Three-Dimensional anatomy of human scarpa's ganglion|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1288/00005537-199209000-00018|last=Sato|first=Hiroaki|last2=Sando|first2=Isamu|date=1992|journal=The Laryngoscope|issue=9|doi=10.1288/00005537-199209000-00018|volume=102|pages=1056–1063|language=en|issn=1531-4995|last3=Takahashi|first3=Haruo}}</ref>。前庭神经节与[[螺旋神经节|螺旋神经节]]（[[听觉|听觉]]）是由同个神经节在早期发育时分裂而来。

